snippet.title: Meteorite's Journey Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Meteorite's Journey is an arcade game where you controle a meteorite who want to travel through the solar system, but the gravity is against you.

Download Meteprite's Journey:
https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.BraveSun.MeteoriteJourney

-Twitter : @bravesun3
